  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想做一个甘特图来对比两种请求处理模式：一种是请求串行执行（one after another），另一种是并行执行（all at once）。这样团队能直观看到性能差异。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sequential",
        "Parallel",
        "Request A",
        "Request B",
        "Request C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那时间轴我们用什么格式？因为都是毫秒级的短时间，我打算用X表示原始毫秒值，axisFormat用%L显示毫秒，这样比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat X",
        "axisFormat %L"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，毫秒级精度够用了。串行部分三个请求各1000ms，Request A从0开始，Request B等A结束后再开始，Request C再往后顺延。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request A",
        "Request B",
        "Request C",
        "0, 1000ms",
        "1000, 2000ms",
        "2000, 3000ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，串行section画好了，三个任务依次排开。我再加一个milestone标记总耗时3000ms。现在画并行部分，三个请求都从0开始同时执行？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Sequential",
        "Total: 3000ms",
        "milestone"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，并行section里三个请求都是0到1000ms，all at once同时发起。最后总耗时应该是1000ms的milestone。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Parallel",
        "0, 1000ms",
        "Total: 1000ms"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。两个section对比很明显：串行那边任务一个接一个，总时间累加到3000ms；并行这边三条线重叠在一起，总时间只有1000ms。标题我用\"Sequential vs Parallel Requests\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Sequential vs Parallel Requests"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "标题没问题。不过我刚注意到，并行section的说明文字应该是\"all at once\"，不是\"at once\"，你帮我确认下？还有串行那边是\"one after another\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Sequential (one after another)",
        "section Parallel (all at once)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "检查过了，两边section的括号说明都正确：Sequential后面是one after another，Parallel后面是all at once。图已经完整了，可以直接拿去给团队演示。",
      "elements_involved": [
